title: Ep - 63 - Spencer Pratt & Chris Manzo
description:
Spencer Pratt reviews the season premiere of Real Housewives of New Jersey and Siesta Key. Julie and Brandy from Dumb, Gay Politics Podcast and People’s Couch review the season premiere of Shark Tank. Chris Manzo from Real Housewives of New Jersey and Manzo’d with Children talks about life on reality television, if he keeps on touch with anyone from Housewives, and his life now. 


Reality Life with Kate Casey
